      {
        title: 'Description:',
        description: `Within my role at ${indiciusUrl}, I played a pivotal part in orchestrating a thorough rebranding endeavor. Leveraging avant-garde technologies, we meticulously crafted a sophisticated and approachable image that appealed to corporate stakeholders and tech enthusiasts.`,
